# Environment Variables

## Required Variables

### Database
DATABASE_URL=postgresql://user:password@host:port/agent_db

### Authentication
JWT_SECRET=your-super-secret-jwt-key-here-change-in-production
JWT_REFRESH_SECRET=your-refresh-token-secret-here-change-in-production
SESSION_SECRET=your-session-secret-here

### Server
PORT=3000
NODE_ENV=development

### Telegram Webhook (Optional for 2FA)
TELEGRAM_WEBHOOK_URL=https://n8n-instance/webhook/...

### Optional
LOG_QUERIES=false

## Example .env file

```env
# Database (agent_db on server)
DATABASE_URL=postgresql://postgres:password@localhost:5432/agent_db

# JWT Secrets (CHANGE THESE IN PRODUCTION!)
JWT_SECRET=super-secret-jwt-key-minimum-32-characters-long
JWT_REFRESH_SECRET=super-secret-refresh-token-key-also-long
SESSION_SECRET=session-secret-for-express-sessions

# Server Configuration
PORT=3000
NODE_ENV=development

# Telegram 2FA
TELEGRAM_WEBHOOK_URL=https://your-n8n-instance/webhook/2fa

# Logging
LOG_QUERIES=false
```

## Production .env

```env
DATABASE_URL=postgresql://user:pass@31.97.62.141:5432/agent_db
JWT_SECRET=<generate-random-64-char-string>
JWT_REFRESH_SECRET=<generate-random-64-char-string>
SESSION_SECRET=<generate-random-64-char-string>
PORT=3000
NODE_ENV=production
LOG_QUERIES=false
```

## Generate Secrets

```bash
# Generate random secrets
node -e "console.log(require('crypto').randomBytes(32).toString('hex'))"
```
